<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Donation Management System - Login</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container mt-4">
        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-4 col-lg-4 offset-md-4 offset-lg-4 mt-4">
                <p class="text-center">
                    This is an example of a donation management system that empowers users to engage in online chat conversations with administrators using socket communication technology.
                </p>
                <p class="text-center">
                    If you've executed the seed command and wish to log in as an administrator, use the email 'admin@gmail.com' and the password 'admin'.
                </p>
                <p class="text-center">
                    Additionally, there's an <a href="/admin">AdminJS application</a> available for donation management. You can log in with the same credentials mentioned above.
                </p>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="email" class="form-label">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" aria-describedby="emailHelp">
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <label for="password" class="form-label">Password</label>
                    <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="login()">Log In</button>
                    <a type="button" class="btn btn-success" href="/users/register">Sign Up</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-center">
                Created by Mateus KÃ¼rten as a project for the FullStack Web Development Postgraduate Program at Instituto Infnet.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="./../js/general.js"></script>
    <script src="./../js/login.js"></script>
</body>

</html>